descriptionHTML:
My Places save and find your present location with one click from your phone or your watch. It also has a google map powered search engine to help you save any locations that interest you for future use.

Are you tired of searching where is your car? Do you need a tool to manage your favorite places? Check out My Places app

Feature:

- Easy to use

- Support Phone and Watch

- Completely Free, NO ads

This app doesn’t collect and send any data. All location informations are saved on your devices and not sent anywhere!

If you like it, please leave your feedback.

Please make sure you have GPS enabled when using this app.
